Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:44.38,OP1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,soreto You Wanna Be My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:51.04,OP1-Romaji,,0,0,0,,We Are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:35.98,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,we're going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:42.42,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:53.81,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:59.24,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,delirious with fever, i take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:05.32,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,if the dusty treasure map has been verified,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:11.19,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:18.06,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,when it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:22.97,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,simply ride aboard someone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.86,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:31.70,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,we're going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:37.88,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:41.12,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,a coin in my pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:44.38,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,and do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:51.04,OP1-English,,0,0,0,,we are!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise the anchor!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the sails!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.15,0:02:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,– Bring the ship forward! \N– You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,– Don't shake things, Sanji! \N– Full speed ahead to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.61,0:02:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're scared, then go down \Nand sleep like a good li'l boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.16,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,D-D-Don't be stupid! \NOf course I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.62,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Breakfast!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.33,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get started on it. \NHold on.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hey, Zoro. Let's play tag.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.31,0:02:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.84,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What, what?! Tag?! \NLet's play, let's play!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys stupid?! \NYou're pathetic, playing at your age!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get some more sleep before breakfast.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?! \N'Cause you don't like losing, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! \NI don't give a damn about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See! You're suddenly mad!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the truth, isn't it?! Bleehhh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you'll join our crew now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm only teaming up \Nwith you, just so you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Always remember that!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.88,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,– I'm over here! Come get me! \N– C'mon, Zoro! Chase me, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing here!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! Your meal's ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Food's on!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! I'm not done with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after he said all that...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks yum!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what do you suppose \Nhappened to Buggy after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.83,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Buggy? Oh, {\i1}that{\i0} Buggy?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? \NMaybe he's at the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are a stubborn lot, \Nevery last one of 'em.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.73,0:04:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who kept \Nchasing me stubbornly! Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hunted pirates for years.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it matters, \Nbut your food's gone, Usopp.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.82,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,– A Special Yogurt Dessert! \N– Luffy! You stole my food again!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,– Oh! Thank you, Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}! \N– Give it back, you idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally finished my flashy raft!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.09,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the great and world-renowned pirate, \NBuggy the Clown-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.73,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\i1}will{\i0} get my crew back together \Nand get my super flashy revenge!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what obstacles lie in my path!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.94,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The score {\i1}must{\i0} be settled!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn flashy rubber man! \NJust you wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.53,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely will beat you senseless \Nand make you cry uncle!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.62,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like this already?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to lose! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:41.15,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,110)}Chase Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:41.15,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,395)\fsp-1}Little Buggy's Big Adventure
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.20,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to make it... to the next island...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not some kind of exhibit, dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...! Are you mocking me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.60,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You got some real guts, ridiculing {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna eatcha!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just feeling hungry, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.03,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made me mad! \NYou're done for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna eat you flashily, \Nso just give yourself up!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop-Chop Cannon!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit your flailing!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.12,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just accept your fate!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.48,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! C'mon!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My plan is flawless!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum! Yum! Yum!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught him!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} got caught?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How did things turn out this way?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! No!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end already?! This sucks!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...! Am I that bad-tasting?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.13,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little bit of a shock!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! A hermit crab!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.18,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when he got on board. \NAt Nami's village?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.89,0:08:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably. \NThat, or maybe at Usopp's village?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, that's incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.86,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd mean he's been traveling with us this whole time!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Why does this happen to me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me? I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.91,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird. \NMust've been my imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy! Quit slackin' off!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am this island's protective god!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this island at once if you value your life!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Protective god?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! You're one of those, uhh...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...weird creatures!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kick your ass, you moron!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! \NJust try taking another step into the forest!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The instant you do, will you \Nreceive my divine punishment
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and meet your doom?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know, you flashy idiot?! \NWhy're you asking me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The animals of this forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.65,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with them, \Nunless you want to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.12,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? \NThese are some flashily interesting animals...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to go any further!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast it! He suddenly shot at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I missed!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,– Come out! \N– Oww! Oww! Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! You have a Devil Fruit power!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.31,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if I do?! You're nothing-
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're-
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}are{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a boxed and sheltered son?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've been overly pampered \Nsince I was just a little boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm not!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do stupid gags!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.12,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't show mercy to {\i1}anyone{\i0} \Nwho messes with them!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You wanna fight {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.09,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I commend your bravery, \Nbut don't blame me after you die!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying weapons are unfair!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's this thing here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.94,0:12:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk so selfishly! \NSay your prayers!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.96,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop-Chop Quick Escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.59,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,– How dare you?! Blast it! Oww! \N– How dare I what?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who messes with the animals has to pay!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're this island's treasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Those weird animals are treasures?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.67,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure refers to gold, silver, \Nand jewels, you flashy idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.26,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to this island to get these animals!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.60,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?! \NI didn't come here 'cause I wanted to!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you're not a poacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! \NI might not look it, but I'm a great pirate!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.19,0:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Buggy the Clown-{\i1}sama{\i0}! \NI'd never do anything as mean as that!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.52,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate? You're a pirate?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.87,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! \NI used to be a pirate a long time ago!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad! My bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a pirate, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.06,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya think? Good, huh?! \NIt's my own unrefined {\i1}sake{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days it's been since I last drank...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.94,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have as many refills \Nas you want! Drink up and up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm really sorry about earlier!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.91,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just assumed you were a poacher \Nwho came to get these animals!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was some horrible stuff you did!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus you let me have this delicious booze, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The only things in this world that \Ninterest me are treasure and alcohol!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm likin' you even more!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pirate, all right!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.30,0:14:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real stout-hearted guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, why are {\i1}you{\i0} on this island?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. \NI originally came here in search of treasure, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! There's treasure on this island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was, I wouldn't be \Nhanging around here, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh. You have a point.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, some stuff happened \Nand my crew left me behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.92,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been calling this island \Nhome for the past 20 years now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,20 years?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.96,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really had it rough!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so bad, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are here with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This way of life is actually pretty \Nnice once you get used to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.44,0:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno. I'd much rather be living \Nthe pirate life with my crew.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.03,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,True, pirate life is nice! It's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.16,0:15:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I would gladly risk my life to \Ngo on treasure-hunting adventures!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?! It's like, "Hurray for pirates!"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.67,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say? When I get my \Npirate crew back, won't you join us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.84,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I greatly welcome guys like you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.39,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you have the pirate spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Whadya say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.06,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... inviting {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.48,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the thought, \Nbut these guys are my friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.82,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When you live with them for \N20 years, they rub off on you,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,even if they are weird creatures.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave them now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was just remembering a young pirate
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.01,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,who asked me to be a pirate \Nagain just like you did.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.23,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so upset, old guy! \NIt's a good thing we came after 20 years!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.19,0:16:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,30 years later and you might've been dead!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such an incredibly nice guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.41,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you and him'd be good friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.12,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. \NSo there {\i1}are{\i0} youngsters out there like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me, though. \NI ran into this one horrible kid!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Assemble! Chop-Chop Parts!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for these?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My parts!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, thief!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go flying, Buggy!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.11,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.61,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how I wound up \Non a wandering journey...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it now \Nmakes me boil with rage!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Sorry to hear what happened...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it just goes to show there are \Nall kinds of youngsters out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's have fun tonight!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want this night to go to waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.51,0:18:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And to us meeting!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.36,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for asking you to help make a raft, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It was my pleasure.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're really going to stay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.87,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. With all my friends here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.83,0:18:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, friend! Take care!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.11,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Buggy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.75,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are many strange \Ncreatures in these waters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be ever careful on your way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I forgot to tell him that!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Run, Buggy!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Look out!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pretty...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's super pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.99,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least it looks like he's saved!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.62,0:20:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He had me sweating bullets there!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.76,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I flashily thought I was a goner there!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Buggy the Clown, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.53,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for a certain man.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn rubber man!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.62,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I {\i1}will{\i0} settle the score with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the guy you're looking for?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. I have a meal ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.90,0:21:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you helped me...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say? \NWill you team up with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not? \NWe both have the same goal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.62,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great. Then cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.00,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.67,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji... Food...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.59,0:22:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You just ate...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.63,0:22:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.57,0:22:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You sleep too much...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.06,0:22:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Help out with work sometimes...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.32,0:22:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.61,0:22:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed they can hold \Nconversations in their sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.28,0:22:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about skillful...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.07,0:22:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll hit the hay, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.25,0:22:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
