Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:31.31,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}doushite konna ni atsui no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:37.49,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}itsu kara ka sonna koto bakari ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:41.32,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}hanarenai yo
