Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:24:02.72,ED2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}issho nara boku wa hashitte yukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:01.79,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}my overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:06.62,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:11.52,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:16.51,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}so keep watching me intently as I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:26.31,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I was thinking about it a bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:31.31,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:37.49,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}starting from some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:41.32,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I haven't been able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:47.64,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I want to catch those feelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:52.47,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}and I'm already about to overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.47,0:23:57.22,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}I want to embrace my dreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:24:02.72,ED2-English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx129.8\fad(150,150)}with you, I can run there
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.42,0:24:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! \NBuggy's henchmen were neat, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.05,0:24:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you mean like the \Nunicycle guy and the lion guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.60,0:24:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cabaji and Mohji, was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.89,0:24:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He had animals, too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.48,0:24:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they really pirates?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.27,0:24:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think is their captain now?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.85,0:24:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cabaji or Mohji, obviously.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.02,0:24:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Maybe it's that lion!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.11,0:24:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.36,0:24:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wait is Over! \NThe Return of Captain Buggy!
